sequenceDiagram
  %% 完成形の1回の memory query シーケンス図: 目的別ルーティングから回答・保留までを見る

  actor User as 人 / AI agent
  participant API as 安定した検索API
  participant Policy as ObjectiveRoutePolicy
  participant Local as local evidence arms
  participant Gate as API Budget Guard
  participant Provider as approved provider arms
  participant Evidence as 根拠化と評価
  participant Trace as Observability

  User->>API: query / objective / context budget
  API->>Trace: request開始
  API->>Policy: 目的別の候補経路を選ぶ
  Policy->>Local: exact / FTS / metadata / relation / media候補
  Local-->>Policy: 復元可能な候補

  opt 承認済みProviderが必要
    Policy->>Gate: 予算・範囲・停止条件を確認
    alt preflight passed
      Gate->>Provider: 最小範囲で実行
      Provider-->>Policy: 追加候補
    else blocked
      Gate-->>Policy: provider_gated
    end
  end

  Policy->>Evidence: Source Bundle / Context Chunk / Citation を作る
  Evidence->>Trace: route・品質・停止理由を保存する

  alt citation-ready
    Evidence-->>API: answer
    API-->>User: 引用付き回答
  else unsupported or conflicting
    Evidence-->>API: abstain / needs_review
    API-->>User: 回答せず理由を返す
  end
